  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h3 style="text-align: left;"><strong>Walk through ancient olive groves, along serene coastlines, across vineyards and around beautiful hilltop towns and villages on an Italian walking holiday - each place has its own unique story to tell.</strong></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13090968/italy-summer-walkers-838x330-hero-generic.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/5455189037d44263918b7ffe84bd68e5" /></p>
<p><img style="width: 0px; height: 0px; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13089361/climate-action-plan-hero-838x330.jpg?width=0&amp;height=0" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/2a04a7d8f96e4ed095539e0430ce5c35" /></p>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Walking Holidays in Italy</h2>
<p>Italy offers mountains, sparkling coastlines, ancient history, and sumptuous cuisine, making it one of the best countries to visit by foot. Hikers, walkers, and anyone who enjoys a riverside stroll will enjoy exploring Italy’s diverse landscapes.</p>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Discover Italy's Best Walking Resorts</h2>
<p>Every region offers something different, so there's plenty to explore and a new adventure awaiting you at every turn. From the towering alpine mountains of the Dolomites to the glistening lakesides, Italy's varied terrain boasts countless secrets that you'll never want to stop seeking out. Italy is home to endless incredible sights that must be seen to be believed.</p>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>Lake Garda</h2>
<p><img src="/media/13089918/lake-garda-501x239.jpg" alt="Lake Garda walking holiday" data-udi="umb://media/0f8d8c5265ad43eb9cab2f2dc0d6650f" /></p>
<p>Italy’s largest lake, <a data-udi="umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473}" title="Lake Garda">Lake Garda</a> has something for everyone.With its contrasting landscape, amazing views, and sleepy villages, it is a fantastic destination for walkers. The walks and hikes here are spectacular, from a casual stroll at the water's edge through to hiking up the highest peak on Mount Baldo.</p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473}" title="Lake Garda" class="c-btn">View Lake Garda holidays</a></div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>The Dolomites</h2>
<p><img src="/media/13089919/dolomites-501x579.jpg" alt="Dolomites walking holiday" data-udi="umb://media/4d0415491d97485b960f0cb6b888c792" /><img style="width: 0px; height: 0px;" src="/media/13089915/lake-annecy-lake-501x239.jpg?width=0&amp;height=0" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/f99fad2fb43f4d48abe5ff0786ec6bec" /></p>
<p>Discover the dramatic mountain landscapes and timeless traditions of the Dolomites. <a data-udi="umb://document/f7e065ba2a3d40d7893ad1b116880496" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f7e065ba2a3d40d7893ad1b116880496}" title="The Dolomites">The Dolomites</a> are a spectacular playground of soaring mountain peaks, meadows bursting with flowers and deep forests. Follow high mountain trails and be rewarded with some of the best views in Italy.</p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/f7e065ba2a3d40d7893ad1b116880496" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f7e065ba2a3d40d7893ad1b116880496}" title="The Dolomites" class="c-btn">View Dolomites holidays</a></div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>Liguria</h2>
<p><img src="/media/13089920/liguria-501x239.jpg" alt="Liguria walking holiday" data-udi="umb://media/013b09159e3b4fe79e7a3447aa395bab" /></p>
<p>The <a data-udi="umb://document/c0a1a2eb5f21493d858ec9013916a8fb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c0a1a2eb5f21493d858ec9013916a8fb}" title="Liguria">Ligurian Riviera</a>, which stretches from the border with France down to Tuscany, is one of the natural wonders of Italy. Endlessly changing scenery makes for some of Europe’s finest coastal walks. Discover a beautiful and varied landscape as you explore ancient paths and long flights of stone steps.</p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/c0a1a2eb5f21493d858ec9013916a8fb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c0a1a2eb5f21493d858ec9013916a8fb}" title="Liguria" class="c-btn">View Liguria holidays</a></div>
</div>
