<h2 style="text-align: left;">Recommended walks in Italy</h2>
<p> </p>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>Sassolungo Group Trail</h3>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/f7e065ba2a3d40d7893ad1b116880496" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f7e065ba2a3d40d7893ad1b116880496}" title="The Dolomites">Dolomites</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13089923/dolomites-mountain-path-314x193.jpg" alt="Dolomites Sassolungo Trail" data-udi="umb://media/7eb8a4d36235442f8b052e7a7d2279d8" /></p>
<p>Enjoy a walk in the UNESCO-protected Dolomite mountain range and admire the famous Sassolungo mountain. Once at the top mountain station continue on to the 'stone city' below Sassolungo. Walk through the high mountain pass, Passo Sella, and enjoy the panoramic views of the Dolomites and Seiser Alm. </p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>Sentieri Rossi</h3>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/c0a1a2eb5f21493d858ec9013916a8fb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c0a1a2eb5f21493d858ec9013916a8fb}" title="Liguria">Liguria</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13089925/walking-italy-hike-mountain-314x193.jpg" alt="Liguria Sentieri Rossi walk" data-udi="umb://media/23b96cfa4db34b48a7e3bae86438b0ee" /></p>
<p>Those who take their hiking seriously should explore the inland red trail, Sentieri Rossi. These trails are usually marked and they tend to be steeper and more challenging than blue designated trails. Admire breath-taking scenery as well as many streams and springs along the route. </p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>Ciclopista del Garda</h3>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473}" title="Lake Garda">Lake Garda</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13089924/cicoplasta-walk-italy-314x193.jpg" alt="Ciclopista del Garda walk" data-udi="umb://media/04fb1c084fcf45ed8de9c7c8fa726f51" /></p>
<p>Beginning from <a data-udi="umb://document/604dbba59ac64320ab6e9f1e89231a4c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/604dbba59ac64320ab6e9f1e89231a4c}" title="Limone">Limone</a>, you can walk along the 2.5 metres wide shared suspended pathway of the Ciclopista del Garda to Riva. The recently opened path provides gorgeous views of Lake Garda from the suspended shared pathway hanging some 50 metres above the lake.</p>
</div>
<p> </p>
</div>
<p> </p>
