<div class="g4">
<p style="color: #003155;"><a data-udi="umb://document/0ef96c55540749d8bc44592840cbb7b4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0ef96c55540749d8bc44592840cbb7b4}?departureDate=04%2F05%2F2022&amp;duration=7&amp;departurePoint=AIRPORT-LGW&amp;adults=2&amp;children=0&amp;brandCode=ING&amp;programCode=GBINB&amp;regionType=29112&amp;id=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000" title="Hotel Europa SkyPool &amp; Panorama" data-anchor="?departureDate=04%2F05%2F2022&amp;duration=7&amp;departurePoint=AIRPORT-LGW&amp;adults=2&amp;children=0&amp;brandCode=ING&amp;programCode=GBINB&amp;regionType=29112&amp;id=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"><strong>Hotel Europa Skypool - 4 Stars</strong></a></p>
<p style="color: #003155;"><a data-udi="umb://document/0ef96c55540749d8bc44592840cbb7b4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0ef96c55540749d8bc44592840cbb7b4}" title="Hotel Europa SkyPool &amp; Panorama"><strong><img style="width: 226x; height: 141px;" src="/media/13078954/hotel-europa-pool.jpg?width=226&amp;height=141" alt="Hotel Europa Skypool" data-udi="umb://media/7cd61e9a0b9c4725a5fb0ac6443012c8" /></strong></a></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473}" title="Lake Garda"><strong>Lake Garda</strong></a></p>
<p>Located in the center of Riva, this hotel is perfectly located to explore the local area and beyond. It offers spectacular views of the harbour and features a rooftop pool. </p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p style="color: #003155;"><a data-udi="umb://document/de7550982a6e4490a203bc261963b533" href="/{localLink:umb://document/de7550982a6e4490a203bc261963b533}?departureDate=01%2F05%2F2022&amp;duration=7&amp;departurePoint=AIRPORT-LGW&amp;adults=2&amp;children=0&amp;brandCode=ING&amp;programCode=GBINB&amp;regionType=29137&amp;id=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000" title="Hotel Meranerhof" data-anchor="?departureDate=01%2F05%2F2022&amp;duration=7&amp;departurePoint=AIRPORT-LGW&amp;adults=2&amp;children=0&amp;brandCode=ING&amp;programCode=GBINB&amp;regionType=29137&amp;id=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"><strong>Hotel Meranahof- 4.5 Stars</strong></a></p>
<p style="color: #003155;"><a data-udi="umb://document/de7550982a6e4490a203bc261963b533" href="/{localLink:umb://document/de7550982a6e4490a203bc261963b533}" title="Hotel Meranerhof"><img style="width: 260px; height: 141px;" src="/media/13076222/1-1.jpg?width=260&amp;height=141" alt="Hotel Meranerhof" data-udi="umb://media/2c9d3d944ff54f7a98f3bdc8d2fce6fd" /></a></p>
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/f7e065ba2a3d40d7893ad1b116880496" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f7e065ba2a3d40d7893ad1b116880496}" title="The Dolomites">The Dolomites </a></strong></p>
<p>This beautiful hotel is surrounded by the Southern Tyrolean mountains. Enjoy the luscious gardens, spa and delicious local cuisine on offer. </p>
</div>
